high_descs: Turn left  and head to the countertop on the other side, specifically the right part of it where you can also see a microwave.
Pick up a soapbar from the countertop.
Turn around, follow a fridge on your left, continue copying the wall on your left until it takes you to an entrance to your left side, where you get in a bathroom, and stand beside a sink.
Place the soapbar inside the sink, rinse it out, and take it out.
Move from the sink to the adjacent toilet.
Put the soapbar on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place the rinsed-out soapbar on toilet
